originalText.text: The portion to price ratio is above and beyond! We all were so full for the portions we received. The drinks were NOT watered down at all. They tasted amazing. The amaretto sour was absolutely delicious. The food was full of flavor. My friend gave me one of his bbq wings and I couldn’t help but salivate lol! They were sweet and tangy. Perfection. I’ve never been so excited about a place like I am for this one. Keep in mind, once everyone at the table receives their food, the service time will be one hour. One hour at the table to finish your food and drink what you can and have ordered. This part at first sucked cause I really wanted to drink more haha but it’s understandable. When we left the line to get in was long! Come around 6pm. Not too many people and right before the rush if you can. Overall, It exceeded my expectations 100%. If you don’t come here, you are missing out on a great place to dine. I can’t wait to come back.

originalText.text: If you are ballin on a budget but want good food and drinks, this is the spot. The drinks are 7 and the apps are all under 10 dollars. The drinks are strong and delicious. The staff here is super friendly. It opens at 5pm but there will be a wait the later you go. Perfect for a pregame or catching up with a friend. 10/10 Highly recommend!

originalText.text: I have no complaints. Unbeatable price. Our server was FANTASTIC. He was so sweet, chill, and impressionable. Portion is JUMBO. This place is a high key throwback to college with the price and portion. The atmosphere is casual and Asian fusion. I love the vibe. The fries are absolutely fantastic and well salted. I can't wait to come back and try everything else. The drinks are totally up my alley since I love sweet and honestly a great size for what your paying for.  If I had to nit pick it be that I wish they would use reusable cups and utensils... the paper waxed cup and plastic utensils is quite odd to me but very wasteful.

originalText.text:
Food is mid. You don’t come here for food. You come here for their drinks. They’re cheap and strong. Effective in getting you to cloud nine haha.
Music is loud here and the staff here are very nice. You will be crowded 3 per 1 table so don’t order too much.
Vibes are great. You’ll have a blast. Get drunk then make your way to 7th street burger and get the double cheeseburger and fries. Thank me later.

originalText.text: This is a cute little spot to grab a bite with friends. The drinks are pretty good. But if this doesn’t convince you to go then I have two words that will. Tater tots! Can’t go wrong with that! Very affordable. The only con to this place is when it is busy it is BUSY. You’ll definitely be waiting to get in during peak hours but it’s worth it.
